{"article_id":"FiNeptyDNDIJ8Pmt","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump sees parallels between Joe Biden ' s early surge to the front of the crowded 2020 Democratic presidential field and his own runaway success in the 2016 Republican primaries .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"In an interview with on Friday afternoon , Trump cast the former vice president as a clear ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"if flawed ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"front runner ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"noting","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"that Biden had recently flubbed the name of Britain ' s prime minister .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"And he compared Biden ' s early success in a heavily crowded field to his own entry and rapid ascent in the 2016 Republican campaign .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"\" I look at it like my race \" in 2016 ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"the president said in a phone interview ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"predicting","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that Biden will remain at the head of the pack of 22 Democrats","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"running for president .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Recalling his June 2015 campaign announcement at Trump Tower ,","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"he boasted ,","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"\" If you remember ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"from the day","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"I came down the escalator until the end of the primaries , I was in the number-one position .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"I was center stage every debate .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"And , you know ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"nobody came close . \"","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Trump actually polled near the bottom of the then twelve-candidate Republican primary field","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"when he first joined the race in mid-June 2015 .","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"But he became the clear GOP front runner within several weeks ,","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"and no other candidate ever decisively claimed that mantle from him .","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"Playbook newsletter","depth":3},{"id":25,"text":"Sign up today","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"to receive the # 1-rated newsletter in politics","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"By signing up","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"Trump appeared to be following Biden ' s early days on the campaign trail closely .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"At one point , he mocked the former vice president for last week","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"mistakenly referring to Margaret Thatcher instead of the current British prime minister , Theresa May .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Biden quickly corrected himself ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"calling it a \" Freudian slip . \"","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"\" Is that a good front runner ?","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"I don ' t know .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"That was a beauty , \"","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"He suggested","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"that he doesn ' t see his other Democratic rivals as serious threats .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"\" It seems that many of them aren ' t registering with ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"you know ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"the public , \"","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Sen. Bernie Sanders","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"( I-Vt. ) ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"he added ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"\" seems to be going in the wrong direction . \"","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Asked specifically about South Bend , Indiana , Mayor Pete Buttigieg ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Trump was dismissive .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"\" Alfred E. Neuman can not become president of the United States , \"","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"he said ,","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"comparing Buttigieg to the iconic boyish Mad Magazine cartoon character .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Asked by in San Francisco on Friday night","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"to respond to Trump 's new nickname ,","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"Buttigieg said :","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"`` I ' ll be honest .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"I had to Google that .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"I guess","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"it ' s just a generational thing .","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"I didn ' t get the reference .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"It 's kind of funny ,","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"I guess .","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"But he ' s also the president of the United States","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"and I ' m surprised","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"he ' s not spending more time","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"trying to salvage this China deal . ''","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"In the 15-minute interview ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"which stemmed from ' s inquiries for a separate story ,","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"the president touched on North Korea , his former campaign aide David Bossie , the Senate Intelligence Committee ' s subpoena to his son , his view of Steve Bannon and Rudy Giuliani ' s upcoming trip to Ukraine .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"Trump again expressed frustration","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"that the Senate Intelligence Committee subpoenaed his oldest son , Donald Trump Jr. ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"to testify as part of the panel ' s ongoing investigation into 2016 Russian election interference .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"But he said","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"he had not spoken to Sen. Richard Burr","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"( R-N.C. ) ,","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"the panel ' s chairman ,","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"who has come under fire from some Republicans","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"for signing off on the subpoena .","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"\" I won the state of North Carolina","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"and frankly had another Republican won [ the primary ] ,","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"they would not have won the state .","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"I have a great relationship to that state .","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"So I was very surprised , \"","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"\" [ Burr ] came in ,","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"ran along with me .","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"I didn ' t know him well","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"but he ran along with me .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"So yeah , I was very surprised","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"to see that . \"","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"The president also gently criticized his former deputy campaign manager and longtime friend David Bossie ,","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"who has been accused of using his political group","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"to scam Republican voters out of millions of dollars for personal financial gain under the guise","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"of supporting Trump ' s re-election .","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"\" I would be disappointed in David","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"if he did that , \"","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"he said ,","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"later adding :","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"\" I would be disappointed","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"if everything wasn ' t on the up and up . \"","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"Trump ' s 2020 campaign issued a sharply-worded statement on Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"that it \" condemns any organization","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"that deceptively uses the President ' s name , likeness , trademarks , or branding","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"and confuses voters. \"","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"The campaign encouraged authorities \" to investigate all alleged scam groups for potential illegal activities . \"","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"Trump said","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"he has not spoken to Bossie about the subject .","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"In a statement , Bossie said ,","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"\" For 15 years we have scrupulously complied with every campaign law and regulation","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"that exists .","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"The accusations are false","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"and personally offensive to me. \"","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"He added","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"that he has \" worked tirelessly","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"to support President Trump and his agenda","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"and I am not going to let smears from old enemies on the left stop me . \"","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"Even amid his apparent anger at one close ally , Trump hinted at a softened view towards a former one :","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"Steve Bannon ,","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"whom Trump excommunicated last year","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"after the strategist was quoted in Michael Wolff ' s incendiary book about the White House , \" Fire and Fury . \"","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"\" Well , I always liked Steve","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"and I mean","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"the last seven months or eight months ,","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"I mean ,","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"you can ' t have nicer statements","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"stated about yourself","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"than the things","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"he ' s been saying about me , \"","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"adding later ,","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"\" You ' ve seen what he ' s said on the various shows","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"and you ' ve seen what he ' s written","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"and it ' s very nice","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"and I appreciate it .","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"But I haven ' t spoken to Steve in a while . \"","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"Trump also touched on the business activities in Ukraine of Joe Biden ' s son , Hunter , a subject","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"that has drawn scrutiny among conservatives in recent days","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"and which Trump ' s personal lawyer , Rudy Giuliani , says","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"should be investigated further .","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"As vice president , Joe Biden pressured Ukraine ' s government to oust a top anti-corruption official","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"who had reportedly investigated a Ukrainian energy company","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"in which Hunter Biden had a financial interest ,","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"although no evidence has emerged","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"that Joe Biden was acting to assist his son ,","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"and it is not clear that the official was probing the company at the time .","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"Trump has also alleged","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"that Ukraine ' s government aided Hillary Clinton ' s 2016 campaign","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"by releasing damaging information about his since-jailed campaign manager , Paul Manafort ,","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"who made millions","depth":14},{"id":153,"text":"doing political work in the country .","depth":14},{"id":154,"text":"Some Democrats have expressed concern","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"that Trump could direct the Justice Department to pursue the allegations ,","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"which they call a diversion from Russia ' s systematic 2016 election meddling ,","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"and warn","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"that it would be an abuse of power for political purposes .","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"When asked whether he would consider directing Attorney General Bill Barr to investigate the Bidens ,","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"as some Democrats fear ,","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"Trump said","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"he had not spoken to Barr about the issue .","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"But he left open the possibility ,","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"saying","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"\" certainly it would be an appropriate thing to \" discuss with Barr . \"","depth":13},{"id":166,"text":"Certainly it is a very big issue","depth":13},{"id":167,"text":"and we ' ll see what happens .","depth":13},{"id":168,"text":"I have not spoken to him about it .","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"Would I speak to him about it ?","depth":14},{"id":170,"text":"I haven ' t thought of that .","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"I mean ,","depth":15},{"id":172,"text":"you ' re asking me a question","depth":16},{"id":173,"text":"I just haven ' t thought of , \"","depth":16},{"id":174,"text":"he said ,","depth":14},{"id":175,"text":"noting","depth":13},{"id":176,"text":"it \" could be a very big situation \" for Biden .","depth":13},{"id":177,"text":"\" Because he ' s a Democrat","depth":14},{"id":178,"text":"it ' s about 1/100 the size of the fact","depth":15},{"id":179,"text":"that","depth":16},{"id":180,"text":"if he were a Republican ,","depth":17},{"id":181,"text":"it would be a lot bigger , \"","depth":17},{"id":182,"text":"he alleged .","depth":13},{"id":183,"text":"Trump also said","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"that he plans to speak to Rudy Giuliani about his personal attorney ' s imminent plans","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"to go to Ukraine","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"to reportedly encourage the Ukrainian president to investigate the origins of the Russia investigation and Hunter Biden ' s role on the board of directors of an energy company","depth":12},{"id":187,"text":"owned by a Ukrainian oligarch .","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"\" I will speak to him about it","depth":12},{"id":189,"text":"before he leaves .","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"I ' m just curious about that , \"","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"he said ,","depth":10},{"id":192,"text":"adding","depth":10},{"id":193,"text":"that he has \" not spoken to him at any great length \" about it .","depth":10},{"id":194,"text":"On foreign policy , the president ,","depth":11},{"id":195,"text":"who once bragged about the cessation of North Korean missile tests during his presidency ,","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"downplayed the significance of North Korea ' s recent decision","depth":11},{"id":197,"text":"to launch a pair of short-range missiles .","depth":11},{"id":198,"text":"\" They ' re short-range","depth":12},{"id":199,"text":"and I don ' t consider that a breach of trust at all .","depth":13},{"id":200,"text":"And , you know ,","depth":15},{"id":201,"text":"at some point I may .","depth":15},{"id":202,"text":"But at this point no , \"","depth":14},{"id":203,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":204,"text":"\" These were short-range missiles and very standard stuff .","depth":11},{"id":205,"text":"Very standard . \"","depth":11},{"id":206,"text":"Trump added","depth":10},{"id":207,"text":"that he might eventually lose faith in his friendly relationship with Kim Jong-un , the North Korean dictator .","depth":10},{"id":208,"text":"\" I mean","depth":11},{"id":209,"text":"it ' s possible that at some point I will ,","depth":12},{"id":210,"text":"but right now not at all , \"","depth":12},{"id":211,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":212,"text":"Minutes before the interview , Trump tweeted","depth":10},{"id":213,"text":"that trade talks with China would continue ,","depth":10},{"id":214,"text":"suggesting","depth":10},{"id":215,"text":"that negotiators were unable to reach a compromise .","depth":10},{"id":216,"text":"Unprompted , the president marveled about the instant effect","depth":10},{"id":217,"text":"his China-related tweet had on stock prices .","depth":10},{"id":218,"text":"\" It seems to be having quite an impact on the market .","depth":10},{"id":219,"text":"I looked","depth":15},{"id":220,"text":"--","depth":15},{"id":221,"text":"the market was down , \"","depth":14},{"id":222,"text":"he said .","depth":13},{"id":223,"text":"\" Now I think","depth":13},{"id":224,"text":"it ' s up 181.44 .","depth":13},{"id":225,"text":"So , it shows you what happens . \"","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":451,"left":249,"right":450,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":249,"left":0,"right":248,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":248,"left":244,"right":247,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":236,"right":243,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":236,"left":230,"right":235,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":230,"left":228,"right":229,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":228,"left":227,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":227,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":229,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":235,"left":6,"right":234,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":234,"left":231,"right":233,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":231,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":233,"left":9,"right":232,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":232,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":243,"left":237,"right":242,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":237,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":242,"left":240,"right":241,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":240,"left":14,"right":239,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":239,"left":238,"right":17,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":238,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":247,"left":245,"right":246,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":245,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":22,"right":23,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":450,"left":255,"right":449,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"